TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: In this mission your objective is to make a tech 2 lab and some tech 2 eco. Then you'll have to kill a big monster who is waiting for you in the east.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Use the metal you reclaim to build a t2 kbot lab here.
You can reclaim rocks, bushes, tree etc. to gain extra resources.
Select the units, click reclaim and then drag and hold the left mouse to reclaim everything within a fixed area.
This is a moho energy converter. It converts excess energy into metal.
Next make an advanced construction kbot and build moho mexes where indicated.
Once you have enough metal income, use your t2 con vehicle to build a fusion here.

TriggerLogic.Message: Now make some t2 units and see if you can kill the monster!
Good work. A second monster awaits in the south east corner :).
